name: LAY ME DOWN: Hinata
description:
Mix media on paper

Hinata is a girl with a bright life as bright as her name. living her life as a rich, pretty, smart and popular girl isn't make her happy at all. She still have an empty side in her heart. Everyone fall in love with her beauty, but she's not even happy with that. For her, the beauty that she had is just a curse, a burden that she can't carries. She always covered her pain with her sweet and bright smile, but every time she's smile, she will got more attention from the others and it's killing her. She always hope that her life gonna end soon, because she tired with the compliment that she got. She didn't mean to be ungrateful, but she just wanna be an ordinary girl who didn't got too much attention. Finally life is just a beautiful pain that she can't resist.
